    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>You know how to work out knotted muscles and relieve tension along iliotibial tracts, bringing nearly instant relief and a rush of endorphins to those under your care. You can spend 10 minutes giving a willing and resting ally a therapeutic sports massage to eliminate any @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.JGFn4MrDZ6X5vrzU]{Fatigue} the creature is currently experiencing, to improve their @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.33ynSbmexuxC3cAQ]{Exhausted} condition to @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.JGFn4MrDZ6X5vrzU]{Fatigued}, or to remove the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.LoRydw1D4bqlbkA2]{Nauseated}, @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.ZacF0l6IwqBwToTJ]{Sickened}, or @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.aAQ6SW6iK0EVq8Ce]{Staggered} condition. A creature can benefit from a therapeutic sports massage only once every 24 hours.</p>"
    },
